event.title: FSFE booth at the 17th „Linuxday“ in Dornbirn, Austria

body.p: The FSFE will be present with a booth organised by the Vienna Fellowship group at the 17th "Linuxday" in Dornbirn in the border region of Austria, Germany, Liechtenstein and Switzerland on November 21, 2015. In three parallel tracks, there will be talks on Free Software for Novices, Experts and Managers.
